AAA Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for Junior Resident Post
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Aug 16, 2025, 15:54 IST
 Government Medical College and Hospital
 6 Jobs |  Posted On : 16-Aug-2025 |  Delhi |  Salary : 56,100 to 177,500




FOLLOW

Aruna Asaf Ali Hospital (AAA) has announced the official notification for 2025. To fill up vacancies for 06 Junior Resident Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the MBBS can grab this chance and apply for the AAA Recruitment 2025. Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested and eligible candidates can attend the interview at the address given below.




If you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more jobs in Delhi.

AAA Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Name of the posts	No.of Vacancies	Qualification
Junior Resident	06	MBBS

Age Limit for the AAA Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 21 years.
The Maximum Age Limit: 40 years.

Selection Process for the AAA Recruitment 2025

Interview

Salary Structure for the AAA Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 56,100 /- per month.
The Maximum Salary: Rs. 1,77,500 /- per month.

Application fee for the AAA Recruitment 2025

There is no application fee.
How to Apply for the AAA Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the recruitment or career page.
Check for the Junior Resident Jobs 2025.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Then, attend the interview at the address given below.

Venue

Office of Medical Superintendent, Aruna Asaf Ali Hospital, 5, Rajpur Road, Delhi 54

Important Dates

Date of Walk-in-Interview	21-08-2025
